Enjoy your movie, Hot Rod.

::Striker::

"Lots of new bots lately," Striker says to Primal, "We just won a battle at 
the Ark."

He lands in front of the Cybertronian Fire, looking around at the miles of 
surrounding Savanah. Pretty good place to crash a ship.

"Welcome to the base, guys," Striker says to Hot Rod and Omega. He turns to 
Omega. "If you really want a mission, go help repair the Ark with the others."
